<br>
I still like EQ very much and look forward to EQ2, but I do wish they would continue to add more single group content.  I LOVED ldon.  I loved veksar (though it was a bit too easy).  I liked the sewer trials in GoD, except for travel to/from and some glitches.  I have no complaints for adding lots and lots of raid content, but I do wish they would continue to add lots and lots of single group content as well.  <br>
<br>
The 2 biggest mistakes ever in EQ are, in order: <br>
1) Complete Heal<br>
2) 70ish person raids.<br>
